# ✨ EduSync – Smart Learning Dashboard

EduSync is a clean, responsive web interface designed to help students and educators organize coursework, track progress, and streamline learning. Built entirely with **HTML** and **CSS**, this project demonstrates how powerful simple web technologies can be when used thoughtfully.

## 🌟 Features

- 📚 Subject-wise content organization  
- ✅ Assignment and progress tracking sections  
- 🎨 Modern, responsive UI with intuitive navigation  
- 🔧 Pure HTML/CSS—no frameworks or JavaScript  
- 🧩 Modular layout for easy customization  

## 📁 Folder Structure
EduSync/ ├── index.html ├── style.css ├── assets/ │ └── images/


## 🚀 Getting Started

To run this project locally:

1. Clone the repository  
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/Mansi30032024/EduSync.git
2. Open index.html in your browser

3. Customize style.css to tweak the design as needed
